::Dollen::

         Dollen sighed as GoldenEye said that his symbol would be blown off.
Oh well.  He respected his title as being a Predacon, but he personally
hated polishing his symbol.  He took his polish and cloth and tossed it over
his shoulder.  He then looked at GoldenEye into her piercing eyes.  She
somehow reminded him of the bot he had visions of.  Could she be a
connection between him and the beautiful bot whom he'd never met??  Is the
bot he has dreams and visions about a Predacon too??  Does she exist???  He
hoped so.

           "Ah, I came here for the excitement, the action, the war!!!!!
Actually, I prefer tactical battle.  Mind over matter, no matter what!!!!
Hey, by the way, could you take me to the Predacon base closest to our
location??" He said, rubbing the back of his head.
